scene.message:
Nanjo: For clothes, my{nl}
uniform is plenty. That, and{nl}
this muffler.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Speaking of clothes,{nl}
what do you make of Nanjo's{nl}
muffler? He's got it{nl}
on all the time.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Did Yuka ask you to{nl}
pick up some clothes? Once{nl}
you're done, we go to the{nl}
hospital!{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: Everyone in this town{nl}
has such bad taste, honestly!{waitkey}The only halfway-decent one{nl}
is a brown-haired boy I see{nl}
sometimes. He wears goggles,{nl}
and he's adorable!{waitkey}{ret}
